    "over_hero": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div style=\"position:relative;background:#061f40;overflow:hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80\" alt=\"Spotwereld\" style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;opacity:0.25\"><div style=\"position:relative;z-index:1;padding:4.5rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\"><div style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;background:rgba(59,130,246,0.2);color:#93c5fd;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;padding:.25rem .875rem;border-radius:9999px;margin-bottom:1rem\">&#9889; OVER ONS</div><h1 style=\"color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);margin:0 0 1rem;line-height:1.2\">Jouw specialist in<br>premium LED verlichting</h1><p style=\"color:#bfdbfe;font-size:1.125rem;margin:0;line-height:1.7\">Bij Spotwereld geloven we dat goede verlichting een ruimte transformeert. Wij leveren topkwaliteit LED producten voor elk interieur &mdash; van inbouwspots tot sfeervolle hanglampen.</p></div></div>",
